{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"58690-tig-s-world","title":"Ụwa Tessy","description":"Ọ bụrụ na ụwa gbara gburugburu, gịnị mere na ndị nọ na ala adaghị a'da? Nne Tessy nwere otu azịza, nna ya nwekwara ihe ọzọ. Ònye na-ekwu eziokwu?","language":"Igbo","langCode":"ig","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nkem Osuigwe"],"illustrators":["Dorian  Dutrieux"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"AfLIA","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/58690-tig-s-world"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83445/size3/ded1f2223f434706a4e13db64f52cb22.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83445/size6/ded1f2223f434706a4e13db64f52cb22.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83123/size6/fc93cb0c81355933a52241f5327fa945.jpg","text":"Nne Tessy bụ ọkà mmụta sayensị.\nỌ maara ihe","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83125/size6/24f99bf1524665dcdb3bbfb82784c677.jpg","text":"Nna Tessy bụ onye edemede.\nỌ na-ede akụkọ","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83127/size6/6f509c13b955dcef8699d5215655b1cb.jpg","text":"4/18","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83128/size6/4f154578ac7f24368f8d02846b153daf.jpg","text":"Tessy nwere  globụ\nnke na-egosi mba ọ bụla n'ụwa.\n\"Mama, ọ bụrụ na ụwa gbara gburugburu, gịnị mere na ndị nọ na ala adaghị a'da?","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83130/size6/a6b1af906e9868ad659a02604a196a74.jpg","text":"\"N'ihi na ike ndọda na-amanye onye ọ bụla n'etiti ụwa.\"","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83132/size6/7f0a24b28c10d5a1a983ba4337de579d.jpg","text":"\"Ebe ọ bụla ị na-aga na ụwa, ewere mmetụta dị ka ọ dị n'okpuru gị.\nỌ gwụla ma ị na-aga mbara igwe. Mgbe ahụ, ọ dịghị ala\nmmetụta dị ka ọ dị n'okpuru gị, ma ị ga na-efegharị! \"","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83134/size6/1cedbc82985927fdc524959910611afc.jpg","text":"\"Ndị nọ n'akụkụ\nụwa \nnke ọzọ na-eche na ha bụ ụzọ maọ bụ na ha dị n'elu","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83135/size6/347d7c2a2e76f82add11d4b4da114949.jpg","text":"... ma n'anyi\ntụgharịa kpodo\nbu isi n'ala! Ọ bụghị ihe ahụ dị ịtụnanya! \"","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83137/size6/fe11c8d649716f7ab2cdeb14dd334d05.jpg","text":"Papa, ọ bụrụ na ụwa gbara gburugburu, gịnị mere na ndị nọ na ala adaghị a'da?","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83139/size6/e9caf704a117e089fde77d8187da05f5.jpg","text":"11/18","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83141/size6/28f8afc01c3904ddf6d22edd33cad0ad.jpg","text":"\"Oh, ha na-eme nke ahụ\nnaogologo oge gara aga! Ọtụtụ ndị dara ada ...","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83142/size6/0ec96b8e5c7245a0dee21b261aaf3f96.jpg","text":"\"...ma daa na gaa Saturn otu mbara igwe.\"","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83144/size6/ed9bc2ee8ca9094d6ab05078b21b6f4f.jpg","text":"\"Ma, ụfọdụ ndị jidere alaka osisi. Ha rịgoro n'elu ala, ma ha gwuru ala ka ha wee gbaa gburugburu n'adaghị ada. \"","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83146/size6/d9e834c8ef052873c1ab61d56f1da3f9.jpg","text":"\"Ugbu a, ha ewuo ụlọ ndị dịka ha akpodoro isi n'ala,\nha ji\nụdọ\nna-agbakwa gburugburu n'etiti\nụlọ  ha niile! \"","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83148/size6/dc6ac1d5e30174f598b0308b21d7e29e.jpg","text":"Tessy ji n'aka na onwe onye na-ekwu akụkọ ụgha.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83149/size6/44e42d9564df02590ca6a3f771ece3ee.jpg","text":"Ma nke ahụ dị mma","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/83151/size6/d3f4b7342d276258ad3d5f94585b50c3.jpg","text":"18/18","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":17,"words":221}}